title: Chicago XXII (22)  Stone of Sisyphus
description:
This album was prepared for Warner Brothers and Reprise records and then they decided they didn&#039;t like Chicago and all the money 16 - 20 brought in and so they shelved it.  It is about to be rereleased and so I&#039;m not sure if it will be counted in the numbering, but it already was as far as the band was concerned -- #22.

This album contains:


All the Years

Stone of Sisyphus

Bigger Than Elvis

Sleeping in the Middle of the Bed Again

Mah Jong

Let&#039;s Take a Lifetime

The Pull

Here With Me

Plaid
